Assignment: You Are the Software Architect
Scenario

You are hired as the lead software architect for a company developing a new smart refrigerator system.
Your team has implemented two versions:
Version A: Inheritance without abstraction (uses instanceof)
Version B: Inheritance with abstraction and polymorphism

The company expects:
The system will grow
New product types will be added frequently
Multiple developers will work on the code
The system must be maintainable for 10+ years
Your task is to choose one version and defend your architectural decision.

Prepare a short architectural defense (written or oral) where you:

1Ô∏è‚É£ Choose Version A or Version B
You must clearly state your choice.
Justify your decision using technical arguments

